{"id":"the-lighthouse-keepers-promise","slug":"the-lighthouse-keepers-promise","title":"The Lighthouse Keeper's Promise","title_ko":"등대지기의 약속","level":"B1","ageBand":"11-13","coverUrl":"/seed/the-lighthouse-keepers-promise/cover.webp","summary_ko":"어떤 밤에도 불을 끄지 않겠다는 약속을 지키려 폭풍과 맞서는 등대지기의 따뜻한 이야기예요.","wordCount":320,"pages":[{"id":"the-lighthouse-keepers-promise-p1","pageNo":1,"spread":"p1","imageUrl":"/seed/the-lighthouse-keepers-promise/p1.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-lighthouse-keepers-promise-p1-s1","ord":0,"text":"On a rocky cliff by the sea stood a tall lighthouse with red and white stripes.","translation_ko":"바닷가 바위 절벽 위에 빨강과 하양 줄무늬가 그려진 키 큰 등대가 서 있었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-lighthouse-keepers-promise/audio/p1-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"On","charStart":0,"charEnd":2,"startMs":0,"endMs":320},{"word":"a","charStart":3,"charEnd":4,"startMs":320,"endMs":620},{"word":"rocky","charStart":5,"charEnd":10,"startMs":620,"endMs":900},{"word":"cliff","charStart":11,"charEnd":16,"startMs":900,"endMs":1280},{"word":"by","charStart":17,"charEnd":19,"startMs":1280,"endMs":1520},{"word":"the","charStart":20,"charEnd":23,"startMs":1520,"endMs":1780},{"word":"sea","charStart":24,"charEnd":27,"startMs":1780,"endMs":1960},{"word":"stood","charStart":28,"charEnd":33,"startMs":1960,"endMs":2400},{"word":"a","charStart":34,"charEnd":35,"startMs":2400,"endMs":2600},{"word":"tall","charStart":36,"charEnd":40,"startMs":2600,"endMs":2940},{"word":"lighthouse","charStart":41,"charEnd":51,"startMs":2940,"endMs":3400},{"word":"with","charStart":52,"charEnd":56,"startMs":3400,"endMs":3960},{"word":"red","charStart":57,"charEnd":60,"startMs":3960,"endMs":4240},{"word":"and","charStart":61,"charEnd":64,"startMs":4240,"endMs":4520},{"word":"white","charStart":65,"charEnd":70,"startMs":4520,"endMs":4720},{"word":"stripes","charStart":71,"charEnd":78,"startMs":4720,"endMs":5080}]},{"id":"the-lighthouse-keepers-promise-p1-s2","ord":1,"text":"Inside lived an old keeper named Elias, who loved the light more than anything.","translation_ko":"그 안에는 엘리어스라는 나이 많은 등대지기가 살았는데, 그는 무엇보다 그 불빛을 아꼈어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-lighthouse-keepers-promise/audio/p1-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Inside","charStart":0,"charEnd":6,"startMs":0,"endMs":600},{"word":"lived","charStart":7,"charEnd":12,"startMs":600,"endMs":1000},{"word":"an","charStart":13,"charEnd":15,"startMs":1000,"endMs":1240},{"word":"old","charStart":16,"charEnd":19,"startMs":1240,"endMs":1620},{"word":"keeper","charStart":20,"charEnd":26,"startMs":1620,"endMs":1860},{"word":"named","charStart":27,"charEnd":32,"startMs":1860,"endMs":2260},{"word":"Elias","charStart":33,"charEnd":38,"startMs":2260,"endMs":2800},{"word":"who","charStart":40,"charEnd":43,"startMs":3200,"endMs":3380},{"word":"loved","charStart":44,"charEnd":49,"startMs":3380,"endMs":3620},{"word":"the","charStart":50,"charEnd":53,"startMs":3620,"endMs":4020},{"word":"light","charStart":54,"charEnd":59,"startMs":4020,"endMs":4120},{"word":"more","charStart":60,"charEnd":64,"startMs":4120,"endMs":4500},{"word":"than","charStart":65,"charEnd":69,"startMs":4500,"endMs":4700},{"word":"anything","charStart":70,"charEnd":78,"startMs":4700,"endMs":5040}]}]},{"id":"the-lighthouse-keepers-promise-p2","pageNo":2,"spread":"p2","imageUrl":"/seed/the-lighthouse-keepers-promise/p2.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-lighthouse-keepers-promise-p2-s1","ord":0,"text":"Every evening, Elias climbed the long stairs and lit the great lamp.","translation_ko":"저녁마다 엘리어스는 긴 계단을 올라가 커다란 등불을 켰어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-lighthouse-keepers-promise/audio/p2-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Every","charStart":0,"charEnd":5,"startMs":0,"endMs":380},{"word":"evening","charStart":6,"charEnd":13,"startMs":380,"endMs":840},{"word":"Elias","charStart":15,"charEnd":20,"startMs":1320,"endMs":1740},{"word":"climbed","charStart":21,"charEnd":28,"startMs":1740,"endMs":2100},{"word":"the","charStart":29,"charEnd":32,"startMs":2100,"endMs":2340},{"word":"long","charStart":33,"charEnd":37,"startMs":2340,"endMs":2700},{"word":"stairs","charStart":38,"charEnd":44,"startMs":2700,"endMs":3080},{"word":"and","charStart":45,"charEnd":48,"startMs":3080,"endMs":3580},{"word":"lit","charStart":49,"charEnd":52,"startMs":3580,"endMs":3680},{"word":"the","charStart":53,"charEnd":56,"startMs":3680,"endMs":3920},{"word":"great","charStart":57,"charEnd":62,"startMs":3920,"endMs":4240},{"word":"lamp","charStart":63,"charEnd":67,"startMs":4240,"endMs":4480}]},{"id":"the-lighthouse-keepers-promise-p2-s2","ord":1,"text":"The warm beam swept across the dark water and helped the ships find their way.","translation_ko":"따뜻한 빛줄기가 어두운 바다를 훑으며 배들이 길을 찾도록 도와주었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-lighthouse-keepers-promise/audio/p2-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"The","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":240},{"word":"warm","charStart":4,"charEnd":8,"startMs":240,"endMs":600},{"word":"beam","charStart":9,"charEnd":13,"startMs":600,"endMs":980},{"word":"swept","charStart":14,"charEnd":19,"startMs":980,"endMs":1380},{"word":"across","charStart":20,"charEnd":26,"startMs":1380,"endMs":1760},{"word":"the","charStart":27,"charEnd":30,"startMs":1760,"endMs":2100},{"word":"dark","charStart":31,"charEnd":35,"startMs":2100,"endMs":2320},{"word":"water","charStart":36,"charEnd":41,"startMs":2320,"endMs":2680},{"word":"and","charStart":42,"charEnd":45,"startMs":2680,"endMs":3220},{"word":"helped","charStart":46,"charEnd":52,"startMs":3220,"endMs":3440},{"word":"the","charStart":53,"charEnd":56,"startMs":3440,"endMs":3980},{"word":"ships","charStart":57,"charEnd":62,"startMs":3980,"endMs":3980},{"word":"find","charStart":63,"charEnd":67,"startMs":3980,"endMs":4360},{"word":"their","charStart":68,"charEnd":73,"startMs":4360,"endMs":4640},{"word":"way","charStart":74,"charEnd":77,"startMs":4640,"endMs":4840}]}]},{"id":"the-lighthouse-keepers-promise-p3","pageNo":3,"spread":"p3","imageUrl":"/seed/the-lighthouse-keepers-promise/p3.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-lighthouse-keepers-promise-p3-s1","ord":0,"text":"Years ago, he had made a promise to every sailor on the coast.","translation_ko":"오래전, 그는 해안의 모든 뱃사람에게 약속을 한 적이 있었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-lighthouse-keepers-promise/audio/p3-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Years","charStart":0,"charEnd":5,"startMs":0,"endMs":340},{"word":"ago","charStart":6,"charEnd":9,"startMs":340,"endMs":680},{"word":"he","charStart":11,"charEnd":13,"startMs":940,"endMs":1060},{"word":"had","charStart":14,"charEnd":17,"startMs":1060,"endMs":1240},{"word":"made","charStart":18,"charEnd":22,"startMs":1240,"endMs":1320},{"word":"a","charStart":23,"charEnd":24,"startMs":1320,"endMs":1480},{"word":"promise","charStart":25,"charEnd":32,"startMs":1480,"endMs":1800},{"word":"to","charStart":33,"charEnd":35,"startMs":1800,"endMs":2120},{"word":"every","charStart":36,"charEnd":41,"startMs":2120,"endMs":2460},{"word":"sailor","charStart":42,"charEnd":48,"startMs":2460,"endMs":2760},{"word":"on","charStart":49,"charEnd":51,"startMs":2760,"endMs":2880},{"word":"the","charStart":52,"charEnd":55,"startMs":2880,"endMs":3000},{"word":"coast","charStart":56,"charEnd":61,"startMs":3000,"endMs":3300}]},{"id":"the-lighthouse-keepers-promise-p3-s2","ord":1,"text":"\"My light will never go dark,\" he told them, \"not even in the wildest storm.\"","translation_ko":"\"내 불빛은 절대 꺼지지 않을 거예요. 아무리 거센 폭풍이 와도요.\" 그가 그들에게 말했어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-lighthouse-keepers-promise/audio/p3-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"My","charStart":1,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":400},{"word":"light","charStart":4,"charEnd":9,"startMs":400,"endMs":760},{"word":"will","charStart":10,"charEnd":14,"startMs":760,"endMs":1120},{"word":"never","charStart":15,"charEnd":20,"startMs":1120,"endMs":1440},{"word":"go","charStart":21,"charEnd":23,"startMs":1440,"endMs":1820},{"word":"dark","charStart":24,"charEnd":28,"startMs":1820,"endMs":2160},{"word":"he","charStart":31,"charEnd":33,"startMs":2440,"endMs":2580},{"word":"told","charStart":34,"charEnd":38,"startMs":2580,"endMs":2800},{"word":"them","charStart":39,"charEnd":43,"startMs":2800,"endMs":3060},{"word":"not","charStart":46,"charEnd":49,"startMs":3440,"endMs":3800},{"word":"even","charStart":50,"charEnd":54,"startMs":3800,"endMs":4140},{"word":"in","charStart":55,"charEnd":57,"startMs":4140,"endMs":4340},{"word":"the","charStart":58,"charEnd":61,"startMs":4340,"endMs":4580},{"word":"wildest","charStart":62,"charEnd":69,"startMs":4580,"endMs":5280},{"word":"storm","charStart":70,"charEnd":75,"startMs":5280,"endMs":5580}]}]},{"id":"the-lighthouse-keepers-promise-p4","pageNo":4,"spread":"p4","imageUrl":"/seed/the-lighthouse-keepers-promise/p4.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-lighthouse-keepers-promise-p4-s1","ord":0,"text":"One autumn night, the wind began to howl and the waves grew taller.","translation_ko":"어느 가을밤, 바람이 울부짖기 시작했고 파도가 점점 높아졌어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-lighthouse-keepers-promise/audio/p4-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"One","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":960},{"word":"autumn","charStart":4,"charEnd":10,"startMs":960,"endMs":1220},{"word":"night","charStart":11,"charEnd":16,"startMs":1220,"endMs":1560},{"word":"the","charStart":18,"charEnd":21,"startMs":1980,"endMs":2080},{"word":"wind","charStart":22,"charEnd":26,"startMs":2080,"endMs":2240},{"word":"began","charStart":27,"charEnd":32,"startMs":2240,"endMs":2540},{"word":"to","charStart":33,"charEnd":35,"startMs":2540,"endMs":2960},{"word":"howl","charStart":36,"charEnd":40,"startMs":2960,"endMs":3080},{"word":"and","charStart":41,"charEnd":44,"startMs":3540,"endMs":3580},{"word":"the","charStart":45,"charEnd":48,"startMs":3580,"endMs":3860},{"word":"waves","charStart":49,"charEnd":54,"startMs":3860,"endMs":3980},{"word":"grew","charStart":55,"charEnd":59,"startMs":3980,"endMs":4260},{"word":"taller","charStart":60,"charEnd":66,"startMs":4260,"endMs":4580}]},{"id":"the-lighthouse-keepers-promise-p4-s2","ord":1,"text":"Rain hammered the windows while thunder rolled across the angry sky.","translation_ko":"비가 창문을 두드렸고 천둥이 성난 하늘을 가르며 굴러갔어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-lighthouse-keepers-promise/audio/p4-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Rain","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":440},{"word":"hammered","charStart":5,"charEnd":13,"startMs":440,"endMs":960},{"word":"the","charStart":14,"charEnd":17,"startMs":960,"endMs":1120},{"word":"windows","charStart":18,"charEnd":25,"startMs":1120,"endMs":1480},{"word":"while","charStart":26,"charEnd":31,"startMs":1480,"endMs":1940},{"word":"thunder","charStart":32,"charEnd":39,"startMs":1940,"endMs":2300},{"word":"rolled","charStart":40,"charEnd":46,"startMs":2300,"endMs":2680},{"word":"across","charStart":47,"charEnd":53,"startMs":2680,"endMs":3000},{"word":"the","charStart":54,"charEnd":57,"startMs":3000,"endMs":3300},{"word":"angry","charStart":58,"charEnd":63,"startMs":3300,"endMs":3500},{"word":"sky","charStart":64,"charEnd":67,"startMs":3500,"endMs":3860}]}]},{"id":"the-lighthouse-keepers-promise-p5","pageNo":5,"spread":"p5","imageUrl":"/seed/the-lighthouse-keepers-promise/p5.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-lighthouse-keepers-promise-p5-s1","ord":0,"text":"Suddenly a bolt of lightning struck the tower with a blinding flash.","translation_ko":"갑자기 번개 한 줄기가 눈부신 빛을 내며 등대를 내리쳤어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-lighthouse-keepers-promise/audio/p5-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Suddenly","charStart":0,"charEnd":8,"startMs":0,"endMs":580},{"word":"a","charStart":9,"charEnd":10,"startMs":800,"endMs":1020},{"word":"bolt","charStart":11,"charEnd":15,"startMs":1020,"endMs":1180},{"word":"of","charStart":16,"charEnd":18,"startMs":1180,"endMs":1700},{"word":"lightning","charStart":19,"charEnd":28,"startMs":1700,"endMs":1700},{"word":"struck","charStart":29,"charEnd":35,"startMs":1700,"endMs":2060},{"word":"the","charStart":36,"charEnd":39,"startMs":2060,"endMs":2380},{"word":"tower","charStart":40,"charEnd":45,"startMs":2380,"endMs":2560},{"word":"with","charStart":46,"charEnd":50,"startMs":2560,"endMs":2900},{"word":"a","charStart":51,"charEnd":52,"startMs":2900,"endMs":3120},{"word":"blinding","charStart":53,"charEnd":61,"startMs":3120,"endMs":3640},{"word":"flash","charStart":62,"charEnd":67,"startMs":3640,"endMs":3940}]},{"id":"the-lighthouse-keepers-promise-p5-s2","ord":1,"text":"The great lamp cracked and went out, and the whole room fell into darkness.","translation_ko":"커다란 등불이 깨지면서 꺼졌고, 방 전체가 어둠에 잠겼어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-lighthouse-keepers-promise/audio/p5-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"The","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":680},{"word":"great","charStart":4,"charEnd":9,"startMs":680,"endMs":980},{"word":"lamp","charStart":10,"charEnd":14,"startMs":980,"endMs":1180},{"word":"cracked","charStart":15,"charEnd":22,"startMs":1180,"endMs":1600},{"word":"and","charStart":23,"charEnd":26,"startMs":1600,"endMs":2020},{"word":"went","charStart":27,"charEnd":31,"startMs":2020,"endMs":2180},{"word":"out","charStart":32,"charEnd":35,"startMs":2180,"endMs":2480},{"word":"and","charStart":37,"charEnd":40,"startMs":3020,"endMs":3040},{"word":"the","charStart":41,"charEnd":44,"startMs":3040,"endMs":3180},{"word":"whole","charStart":45,"charEnd":50,"startMs":3180,"endMs":3500},{"word":"room","charStart":51,"charEnd":55,"startMs":3500,"endMs":3720},{"word":"fell","charStart":56,"charEnd":60,"startMs":3720,"endMs":4000},{"word":"into","charStart":61,"charEnd":65,"startMs":4000,"endMs":4280},{"word":"darkness","charStart":66,"charEnd":74,"startMs":4280,"endMs":4540}]}]},{"id":"the-lighthouse-keepers-promise-p6","pageNo":6,"spread":"p6","imageUrl":"/seed/the-lighthouse-keepers-promise/p6.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-lighthouse-keepers-promise-p6-s1","ord":0,"text":"Elias felt his heart sink, because he knew ships were still out at sea.","translation_ko":"엘리어스는 바다에 아직 배들이 떠 있다는 걸 알았기에 가슴이 철렁 내려앉았어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-lighthouse-keepers-promise/audio/p6-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Elias","charStart":0,"charEnd":5,"startMs":0,"endMs":520},{"word":"felt","charStart":6,"charEnd":10,"startMs":520,"endMs":760},{"word":"his","charStart":11,"charEnd":14,"startMs":760,"endMs":960},{"word":"heart","charStart":15,"charEnd":20,"startMs":960,"endMs":1240},{"word":"sink","charStart":21,"charEnd":25,"startMs":1240,"endMs":1580},{"word":"because","charStart":27,"charEnd":34,"startMs":1580,"endMs":2120},{"word":"he","charStart":35,"charEnd":37,"startMs":2120,"endMs":2300},{"word":"knew","charStart":38,"charEnd":42,"startMs":2300,"endMs":2540},{"word":"ships","charStart":43,"charEnd":48,"startMs":2540,"endMs":2780},{"word":"were","charStart":49,"charEnd":53,"startMs":2780,"endMs":3080},{"word":"still","charStart":54,"charEnd":59,"startMs":3080,"endMs":3280},{"word":"out","charStart":60,"charEnd":63,"startMs":3280,"endMs":3440},{"word":"at","charStart":64,"charEnd":66,"startMs":3440,"endMs":3680},{"word":"sea","charStart":67,"charEnd":70,"startMs":3680,"endMs":3800}]},{"id":"the-lighthouse-keepers-promise-p6-s2","ord":1,"text":"\"I made a promise,\" he whispered, \"and I will keep it tonight.\"","translation_ko":"\"나는 약속을 했어. 오늘 밤 반드시 지킬 거야.\" 그가 작게 속삭였어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-lighthouse-keepers-promise/audio/p6-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"I","charStart":1,"charEnd":2,"startMs":0,"endMs":180},{"word":"made","charStart":3,"charEnd":7,"startMs":180,"endMs":340},{"word":"a","charStart":8,"charEnd":9,"startMs":340,"endMs":520},{"word":"promise","charStart":10,"charEnd":17,"startMs":520,"endMs":920},{"word":"he","charStart":20,"charEnd":22,"startMs":1240,"endMs":1400},{"word":"whispered","charStart":23,"charEnd":32,"startMs":1400,"endMs":1860},{"word":"and","charStart":35,"charEnd":38,"startMs":2280,"endMs":2360},{"word":"I","charStart":39,"charEnd":40,"startMs":2360,"endMs":2480},{"word":"will","charStart":41,"charEnd":45,"startMs":2480,"endMs":2660},{"word":"keep","charStart":46,"charEnd":50,"startMs":2660,"endMs":2820},{"word":"it","charStart":51,"charEnd":53,"startMs":2820,"endMs":3000},{"word":"tonight","charStart":54,"charEnd":61,"startMs":3000,"endMs":3340}]}]},{"id":"the-lighthouse-keepers-promise-p7","pageNo":7,"spread":"p7","imageUrl":"/seed/the-lighthouse-keepers-promise/p7.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-lighthouse-keepers-promise-p7-s1","ord":0,"text":"He hurried down to the storeroom and gathered every lantern he could find.","translation_ko":"그는 서둘러 창고로 내려가 찾을 수 있는 등불을 모조리 끌어모았어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-lighthouse-keepers-promise/audio/p7-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"He","charStart":0,"charEnd":2,"startMs":0,"endMs":260},{"word":"hurried","charStart":3,"charEnd":10,"startMs":260,"endMs":640},{"word":"down","charStart":11,"charEnd":15,"startMs":640,"endMs":980},{"word":"to","charStart":16,"charEnd":18,"startMs":980,"endMs":1100},{"word":"the","charStart":19,"charEnd":22,"startMs":1100,"endMs":1340},{"word":"storeroom","charStart":23,"charEnd":32,"startMs":1340,"endMs":1900},{"word":"and","charStart":33,"charEnd":36,"startMs":1900,"endMs":2160},{"word":"gathered","charStart":37,"charEnd":45,"startMs":2160,"endMs":2420},{"word":"every","charStart":46,"charEnd":51,"startMs":2420,"endMs":3040},{"word":"lantern","charStart":52,"charEnd":59,"startMs":3040,"endMs":3380},{"word":"he","charStart":60,"charEnd":62,"startMs":3380,"endMs":3620},{"word":"could","charStart":63,"charEnd":68,"startMs":3620,"endMs":3800},{"word":"find","charStart":69,"charEnd":73,"startMs":3800,"endMs":4120}]},{"id":"the-lighthouse-keepers-promise-p7-s2","ord":1,"text":"One by one, he carried them up and set them glowing in the high window.","translation_ko":"하나씩 하나씩 위로 들고 올라가, 높은 창가에 환히 밝혀 놓았어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-lighthouse-keepers-promise/audio/p7-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"One","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":280},{"word":"by","charStart":4,"charEnd":6,"startMs":280,"endMs":500},{"word":"one","charStart":7,"charEnd":10,"startMs":500,"endMs":1020},{"word":"he","charStart":12,"charEnd":14,"startMs":1180,"endMs":1360},{"word":"carried","charStart":15,"charEnd":22,"startMs":1360,"endMs":1640},{"word":"them","charStart":23,"charEnd":27,"startMs":1640,"endMs":1840},{"word":"up","charStart":28,"charEnd":30,"startMs":1840,"endMs":2040},{"word":"and","charStart":31,"charEnd":34,"startMs":2040,"endMs":2340},{"word":"set","charStart":35,"charEnd":38,"startMs":2340,"endMs":2500},{"word":"them","charStart":39,"charEnd":43,"startMs":2500,"endMs":2700},{"word":"glowing","charStart":44,"charEnd":51,"startMs":2700,"endMs":3040},{"word":"in","charStart":52,"charEnd":54,"startMs":3040,"endMs":3320},{"word":"the","charStart":55,"charEnd":58,"startMs":3320,"endMs":3440},{"word":"high","charStart":59,"charEnd":63,"startMs":3440,"endMs":3740},{"word":"window","charStart":64,"charEnd":70,"startMs":3740,"endMs":4020}]}]},{"id":"the-lighthouse-keepers-promise-p8","pageNo":8,"spread":"p8","imageUrl":"/seed/the-lighthouse-keepers-promise/p8.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-lighthouse-keepers-promise-p8-s1","ord":0,"text":"When the lanterns burned low, Elias did not give up.","translation_ko":"등불이 점점 사그라들었지만 엘리어스는 포기하지 않았어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-lighthouse-keepers-promise/audio/p8-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"When","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":240},{"word":"the","charStart":5,"charEnd":8,"startMs":240,"endMs":480},{"word":"lanterns","charStart":9,"charEnd":17,"startMs":480,"endMs":1020},{"word":"burned","charStart":18,"charEnd":24,"startMs":1020,"endMs":1200},{"word":"low","charStart":25,"charEnd":28,"startMs":1200,"endMs":1580},{"word":"Elias","charStart":30,"charEnd":35,"startMs":1960,"endMs":2340},{"word":"did","charStart":36,"charEnd":39,"startMs":2340,"endMs":2600},{"word":"not","charStart":40,"charEnd":43,"startMs":2600,"endMs":2900},{"word":"give","charStart":44,"charEnd":48,"startMs":2900,"endMs":3080},{"word":"up","charStart":49,"charEnd":51,"startMs":3080,"endMs":3300}]},{"id":"the-lighthouse-keepers-promise-p8-s2","ord":1,"text":"He took the small candle from beside his own bed and held it to the glass.","translation_ko":"그는 자기 침대 곁의 작은 촛불을 집어 들어 유리창에 가까이 댔어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-lighthouse-keepers-promise/audio/p8-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"He","charStart":0,"charEnd":2,"startMs":0,"endMs":180},{"word":"took","charStart":3,"charEnd":7,"startMs":180,"endMs":380},{"word":"the","charStart":8,"charEnd":11,"startMs":380,"endMs":580},{"word":"small","charStart":12,"charEnd":17,"startMs":580,"endMs":960},{"word":"candle","charStart":18,"charEnd":24,"startMs":960,"endMs":1260},{"word":"from","charStart":25,"charEnd":29,"startMs":1260,"endMs":1520},{"word":"beside","charStart":30,"charEnd":36,"startMs":1520,"endMs":1840},{"word":"his","charStart":37,"charEnd":40,"startMs":1840,"endMs":2020},{"word":"own","charStart":41,"charEnd":44,"startMs":2020,"endMs":2320},{"word":"bed","charStart":45,"charEnd":48,"startMs":2320,"endMs":2540},{"word":"and","charStart":49,"charEnd":52,"startMs":2540,"endMs":3100},{"word":"held","charStart":53,"charEnd":57,"startMs":3100,"endMs":3260},{"word":"it","charStart":58,"charEnd":60,"startMs":3260,"endMs":3420},{"word":"to","charStart":61,"charEnd":63,"startMs":3420,"endMs":3500},{"word":"the","charStart":64,"charEnd":67,"startMs":3500,"endMs":3680},{"word":"glass","charStart":68,"charEnd":73,"startMs":3680,"endMs":3960}]}]},{"id":"the-lighthouse-keepers-promise-p9","pageNo":9,"spread":"p9","imageUrl":"/seed/the-lighthouse-keepers-promise/p9.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-lighthouse-keepers-promise-p9-s1","ord":0,"text":"Far out on the black water, the sailors on a fishing boat were lost and frightened.","translation_ko":"저 멀리 캄캄한 바다 위에서 고깃배의 뱃사람들이 길을 잃고 겁에 질려 있었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-lighthouse-keepers-promise/audio/p9-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Far","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":380},{"word":"out","charStart":4,"charEnd":7,"startMs":380,"endMs":680},{"word":"on","charStart":8,"charEnd":10,"startMs":680,"endMs":840},{"word":"the","charStart":11,"charEnd":14,"startMs":840,"endMs":980},{"word":"black","charStart":15,"charEnd":20,"startMs":980,"endMs":1280},{"word":"water","charStart":21,"charEnd":26,"sta