text":"Then they saw a tiny golden glow shining bravely through the rain.","translation_ko":"바로 그때, 빗속을 뚫고 용감하게 빛나는 작은 황금빛이 그들 눈에 들어왔어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-lighthouse-keepers-promise/audio/p10-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Then","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":780},{"word":"they","charStart":5,"charEnd":9,"startMs":780,"endMs":1240},{"word":"saw","charStart":10,"charEnd":13,"startMs":1240,"endMs":1480},{"word":"a","charStart":14,"charEnd":15,"startMs":1480,"endMs":2060},{"word":"tiny","charStart":16,"charEnd":20,"startMs":2060,"endMs":2080},{"word":"golden","charStart":21,"charEnd":27,"startMs":2080,"endMs":2460},{"word":"glow","charStart":28,"charEnd":32,"startMs":2460,"endMs":2820},{"word":"shining","charStart":33,"charEnd":40,"startMs":2820,"endMs":3500},{"word":"bravely","charStart":41,"charEnd":48,"startMs":3500,"endMs":4160},{"word":"through","charStart":49,"charEnd":56,"startMs":4160,"endMs":4540},{"word":"the","charStart":57,"charEnd":60,"startMs":4540,"endMs":4860},{"word":"rain","charStart":61,"charEnd":65,"startMs":4860,"endMs":4920}]},{"id":"the-lighthouse-keepers-promise-p10-s2","ord":1,"text":"\"The lighthouse!\" they shouted, and turned their boat toward the light.","translation_ko":"\"등대다!\" 그들이 외치며 배를 그 불빛 쪽으로 돌렸어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-lighthouse-keepers-promise/audio/p10-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"The","charStart":1,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":280},{"word":"lighthouse","charStart":5,"charEnd":15,"startMs":280,"endMs":720},{"word":"they","charStart":18,"charEnd":22,"startMs":920,"endMs":1040},{"word":"shouted","charStart":23,"charEnd":30,"startMs":1040,"endMs":1320},{"word":"and","charStart":32,"charEnd":35,"startMs":1560,"endMs":2000},{"word":"turned","charStart":36,"charEnd":42,"startMs":2000,"endMs":2220},{"word":"their","charStart":43,"charEnd":48,"startMs":2220,"endMs":2500},{"word":"boat","charStart":49,"charEnd":53,"startMs":2500,"endMs":2780},{"word":"toward","charStart":54,"charEnd":60,"startMs":2780,"endMs":3100},{"word":"the","charStart":61,"charEnd":64,"startMs":3100,"endMs":3320},{"word":"light","charStart":65,"charEnd":70,"startMs":3320,"endMs":3520}]}]},{"id":"the-lighthouse-keepers-promise-p11","pageNo":11,"spread":"p11","imageUrl":"/seed/the-lighthouse-keepers-promise/p11.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-lighthouse-keepers-promise-p11-s1","ord":0,"text":"Slowly and carefully, the little boat found its way back to the safe harbor.","translation_ko":"느리지만 조심스럽게, 작은 배는 안전한 항구로 되돌아오는 길을 찾았어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-lighthouse-keepers-promise/audio/p11-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Slowly","charStart":0,"charEnd":6,"startMs":0,"endMs":640},{"word":"and","charStart":7,"charEnd":10,"startMs":640,"endMs":1100},{"word":"carefully","charStart":11,"charEnd":20,"startMs":1100,"endMs":1560},{"word":"the","charStart":22,"charEnd":25,"startMs":2100,"endMs":2260},{"word":"little","charStart":26,"charEnd":32,"startMs":2260,"endMs":2480},{"word":"boat","charStart":33,"charEnd":37,"startMs":2480,"endMs":2660},{"word":"found","charStart":38,"charEnd":43,"startMs":2660,"endMs":2960},{"word":"its","charStart":44,"charEnd":47,"startMs":2960,"endMs":3180},{"word":"way","charStart":48,"charEnd":51,"startMs":3180,"endMs":3360},{"word":"back","charStart":52,"charEnd":56,"startMs":3360,"endMs":3620},{"word":"to","charStart":57,"charEnd":59,"startMs":3620,"endMs":3740},{"word":"the","charStart":60,"charEnd":63,"startMs":3740,"endMs":4080},{"word":"safe","charStart":64,"charEnd":68,"startMs":4080,"endMs":4200},{"word":"harbor","charStart":69,"charEnd":75,"startMs":4200,"endMs":4440}]},{"id":"the-lighthouse-keepers-promise-p11-s2","ord":1,"text":"When the storm finally passed, a soft pink morning rose over the calm sea.","translation_ko":"마침내 폭풍이 지나가자, 잔잔한 바다 위로 부드러운 분홍빛 아침이 떠올랐어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-lighthouse-keepers-promise/audio/p11-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"When","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":320},{"word":"the","charStart":5,"charEnd":8,"startMs":320,"endMs":820},{"word":"storm","charStart":9,"charEnd":14,"startMs":820,"endMs":980},{"word":"finally","charStart":15,"charEnd":22,"startMs":980,"endMs":1660},{"word":"passed","charStart":23,"charEnd":29,"startMs":1660,"endMs":2120},{"word":"a","charStart":31,"charEnd":32,"startMs":2820,"endMs":3000},{"word":"soft","charStart":33,"charEnd":37,"startMs":3000,"endMs":3260},{"word":"pink","charStart":38,"charEnd":42,"startMs":3260,"endMs":3620},{"word":"morning","charStart":43,"charEnd":50,"startMs":3620,"endMs":3980},{"word":"rose","charStart":51,"charEnd":55,"startMs":3980,"endMs":4400},{"word":"over","charStart":56,"charEnd":60,"startMs":4400,"endMs":4620},{"word":"the","charStart":61,"charEnd":64,"startMs":4620,"endMs":5040},{"word":"calm","charStart":65,"charEnd":69,"startMs":5040,"endMs":5100},{"word":"sea","charStart":70,"charEnd":73,"startMs":5100,"endMs":5440}]}]},{"id":"the-lighthouse-keepers-promise-p12","pageNo":12,"spread":"p12","imageUrl":"/seed/the-lighthouse-keepers-promise/p12.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-lighthouse-keepers-promise-p12-s1","ord":0,"text":"The grateful sailors climbed the cliff to thank the tired old keeper.","translation_ko":"고마운 마음에 뱃사람들이 절벽을 올라와 지친 노인에게 감사 인사를 전했어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-lighthouse-keepers-promise/audio/p12-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"The","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":720},{"word":"grateful","charStart":4,"charEnd":12,"startMs":720,"endMs":1220},{"word":"sailors","charStart":13,"charEnd":20,"startMs":1220,"endMs":1660},{"word":"climbed","charStart":21,"charEnd":28,"startMs":1660,"endMs":2180},{"word":"the","charStart":29,"charEnd":32,"startMs":2180,"endMs":2440},{"word":"cliff","charStart":33,"charEnd":38,"startMs":2440,"endMs":2740},{"word":"to","charStart":39,"charEnd":41,"startMs":2740,"endMs":3120},{"word":"thank","charStart":42,"charEnd":47,"startMs":3120,"endMs":3300},{"word":"the","charStart":48,"charEnd":51,"startMs":3300,"endMs":3620},{"word":"tired","charStart":52,"charEnd":57,"startMs":3620,"endMs":3820},{"word":"old","charStart":58,"charEnd":61,"startMs":3820,"endMs":4080},{"word":"keeper","charStart":62,"charEnd":68,"startMs":4080,"endMs":4340}]},{"id":"the-lighthouse-keepers-promise-p12-s2","ord":1,"text":"Elias only smiled and said, \"A promise is a light that must never go out.\"","translation_ko":"엘리어스는 그저 빙긋 웃으며 말했어요. \"약속이란 결코 꺼져선 안 되는 불빛이란다.\"","audioUrl":"/seed/the-lighthouse-keepers-promise/audio/p12-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Elias","charStart":0,"charEnd":5,"startMs":0,"endMs":480},{"word":"only","charStart":6,"charEnd":10,"startMs":480,"endMs":880},{"word":"smiled","charStart":11,"charEnd":17,"startMs":880,"endMs":1220},{"word":"and","charStart":18,"charEnd":21,"startMs":1220,"endMs":1580},{"word":"said","charStart":22,"charEnd":26,"startMs":1580,"endMs":1720},{"word":"A","charStart":29,"charEnd":30,"startMs":2280,"endMs":2420},{"word":"promise","charStart":31,"charEnd":38,"startMs":2420,"endMs":2740},{"word":"is","charStart":39,"charEnd":41,"startMs":2740,"endMs":2940},{"word":"a","charStart":42,"charEnd":43,"startMs":2940,"endMs":3160},{"word":"light","charStart":44,"charEnd":49,"startMs":3160,"endMs":3320},{"word":"that","charStart":50,"charEnd":54,"startMs":3320,"endMs":3600},{"word":"must","charStart":55,"charEnd":59,"startMs":3600,"endMs":3760},{"word":"never","charStart":60,"charEnd":65,"startMs":3760,"endMs":3980},{"word":"go","charStart":66,"charEnd":68,"startMs":3980,"endMs":4220},{"word":"out","charStart":69,"charEnd":72,"startMs":4220,"endMs":4400}]}]}],"quiz":[{"question_ko":"엘리어스가 뱃사람들에게 한 약속은 무엇이었나요?","type":"mc","options":["불빛을 절대 끄지 않겠다는 약속","새 등대를 짓겠다는 약속","매일 생선을 잡겠다는 약속","배를 직접 만들겠다는 약속"],"answerIndex":0,"explain_ko":"그는 아무리 거센 폭풍에도 등대 불을 끄지 않겠다고 약속했어요.","id":"the-lighthouse-keepers-promise-q1","ord":0},{"question_ko":"커다란 등불이 꺼진 까닭은 무엇인가요?","type":"mc","options":["바람이 창문을 열어서","엘리어스가 깜빡 잠들어서","기름이 다 떨어져서","번개가 등대를 내리쳐서"],"answerIndex":3,"explain_ko":"번개가 등대를 내리치면서 커다란 등불이 깨지고 꺼졌어요.","id":"the-lighthouse-keepers-promise-q2","ord":1},{"question_ko":"등불이 깨진 뒤 엘리어스가 가장 먼저 한 일은 무엇인가요?","type":"mc","options":["창고에서 등불을 모아 왔다","배를 타고 바다로 나갔다","잠자리에 들었다","사람들을 부르러 나갔다"],"answerIndex":0,"explain_ko":"그는 창고로 내려가 찾을 수 있는 등불을 모두 모아 창가에 밝혔어요.","id":"the-lighthouse-keepers-promise-q3","ord":2},{"question_ko":"길 잃은 고깃배는 마침내 어떻게 되었나요?","type":"mc","options":["바위에 부딪혀 부서졌다","다른 나라로 떠내려갔다","안전한 항구로 돌아왔다","바다에서 사라졌다"],"answerIndex":2,"explain_ko":"작은 불빛을 보고 방향을 잡은 배는 안전한 항구로 무사히 돌아왔어요.","id":"the-lighthouse-keepers-promise-q4","ord":3},{"question_ko":"이 이야기가 전하려는 마음은 무엇일까요?","type":"mc","options":["한 번 한 약속은 끝까지 지켜야 한다","혼자 일하는 것이 가장 좋다","바다는 늘 위험하니 피해야 한다","등대는 오래되면 바꿔야 한다"],"answerIndex":0,"explain_ko":"엘리어스가 끝까지 불을 지킨 모습은 약속을 지키는 마음의 소중함을 보여 줘요.","id":"the-lighthouse-keepers-promise-q5","ord":4}]}